\section*{Summary}
LLM systems engineer focused on improving reasoning performance and cost-efficiency through synthetic data generation, structured tool-use training, and rigorous evaluation. Experienced in designing end-to-end pipelines spanning data collection, dataset QA, training/eval harnesses, deployment, and incident-style debugging. Strong bias toward reproducible measurement, leakage controls, and honest baselines.

